title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre eager to move past a fear that continues to hold you back. An unpleasant situation could emerge that initially triggers you to apply the brakes now. However, you may discover that youre more than ready to move forward if you face your resistance head on today. The comfort-loving Cancer Moon tensely opposes unrelenting Pluto to jettison you out of your own inertia and into action. It doesnt matter how big or small the victory; one good jab against panic can lead to another. Actress Madeline Brewer said, Step outside your comfort zone because thats the only way youre going to grow. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
